{"tid":785839,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發奇想】我一個人去左台灣金門打工換宿嘅小文青之旅","createTime":"2018-08-19T13:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T14:45:00.000Z","uid":79190,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f040fce3fece26650681f3adee0c302f6d047efb","tid":785839,"uid":79190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"平時都係做開CD rom，但係琴日啱啱喺金門返黎有感而發，特登開左個post打呢篇文遊記當係自己嘅回憶都比各位巴打參考下啦<br />\n<br />\n作為小毒毒嘅我，係香港成日都係匿係屋企唔出街，平時嘅興趣最多就係打下機睇下動畫<br />\n所以上左大學之後一直有個夢想係去第二個地方識一班完全陌生嘅人，係一個陌生嘅環境開展新嘅生活<br />\n<br />\n因為自己平時都會獨遊，住過唔少青年旅舍，知道台灣呢邊嘅青年旅舍好興打工換宿，既可以唔洗錢係青年旅舍住15-30日，玩盡曬當地嘅景點，又會有唔少大學生一齊玩。所以我今個暑假就終於立下決心去台灣嘅金門島打工換宿啦 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/eJ0hSe/1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FeJ0hSe%2F1.png&h=ad3b5294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺金門隨時都會影到靚相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/eicU7e/3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FeicU7e%2F3.png&h=80d08105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係國旗呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/haYxtK/4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FhaYxtK%2F4.png&h=e0c4f9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度就係一個充滿著濃濃戰地色彩嘅地方"},{"pid":"a7571fa8b00385c6d8e05ee6a32648a29b112547","tid":785839,"uid":79190,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"點解我揀金門呢？<br />\n<br />\n相信好多人聽到金門第一個反應就係wow 大公司黎嘅，去金門做幾有前途呀～<br />\n其實金門係一個台灣管轄嘅外島，喺台灣人嘅眼中係前線中嘅最前線<br />\n因為佢距離中共管治嘅邊界最近只有2公里，天氣好嘅時候甚至可以用肉眼望到廈門嘅高樓大廈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/mhFrne/5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FmhFrne%2F5.png&h=d5328c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsor影得唔好 對面廈門嘅高樓大廈真係用肉眼就可以睇到<br />\n<br />\n我自己由細到大都係好反共嘅，而家見到中共施予香港嘅咁多制肘，逐步逐步用金權剝奪香港嘅自由民主更加係又悲憤又無力<br />\n<br />\n可能係因為咁所以我更加鍾意台灣，連登仔嘅眼中台灣可能只係有新北市嘅豐功偉績，但係真心嘅，我覺得佢哋作為華人世界第一個民主嘅國家好值得我地去學習佢地對威權嘅態度，佢地嘅民主制度同埋公民社會<br />\n<br />\n就因為咁我就揀左台灣面對中共嘅最前線金門啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/hsBgne/6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FhsBgne%2F6.png&h=15b2c2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前鄧麗君就係裡面呼籲共軍游水過黎投降，往事已矣～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/buvJYK/7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FbuvJYK%2F7.png&h=574ec4bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翟山小艇坑道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/jHdoYK/8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FjHdoYK%2F8.png&h=09029100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁多國軍嘅精神標語，而家已經變曬景點"},{"pid":"1d68a9344a30e0066031d66890064fef79825b87","tid":785839,"uid":49353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打去打工換宿係到咗埗先搵？"},{"pid":"2f47fca21b91670e72eba8771d62730d0c3a229c","tid":785839,"uid":115184,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"金門唔喺台灣，喺福建"},{"pid":"a1fac3ba9bde28c5454a3f9c5997a3985850a10f","tid":785839,"uid":79190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d68a9344a30e0066031d66890064fef79825b87","tid":785839,"uid":49353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打去打工換宿係到咗埗先搵？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"通常都要早啲嘅<br />\n好似我今次要三月就遞CV比個老世話要8月黎"},{"pid":"38cc3e0b54852e322feaaf39ed7ed2d983ee1c86","tid":785839,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:06:09.000Z","msg":"打工換宿合法?"},{"pid":"22ac7aa4a44f77e87768608f277c47aa818b9dd7","tid":785839,"uid":202351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"8d165400e2d7ac9405a7ac58cd5e50a16f6f3c85","tid":785839,"uid":37220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">毋亡在莒</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bf40716bb5f7135da5fadd9d0df5bff394b72fe4","tid":785839,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"22ef38f5a8d984f2c1692a80427b73dc0e7d4088","tid":785839,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"c4709ff9b6d4966197dd4232e9e43cfb90632fe6","tid":785839,"uid":79190,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"2f47fca21b91670e72eba8771d62730d0c3a229c","tid":785839,"uid":115184,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"金門唔喺台灣，喺福建"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"同意！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n金門係中華民國嘅福建省嘅🇹🇼"},{"pid":"cc9d63f363d06f98be584ce2ba24ee9e0a1f1782","tid":785839,"uid":81106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:57:14.000Z","msg":"去過四日三夜，小島風情，本地人甚至再友善過台灣人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fb0a14b3df22a0662aefd07d204cfa5b2b8f78","tid":785839,"uid":26159,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T19:25:12.000Z","msg":"巴打識唔識騎車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁方便<br />\n好鍾意金門   之前都諗住再去打工換宿 <br />\n但因為唔識騎車放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一定要撩人吹水<br />\n有好多呀叔會帶埋仔女返金門懷緬<br />\n勁多故仔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有記得食好出名個間蚵嗲   正到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64d9e94a73c1fac40917d3df16f7c000d3eae8f","tid":785839,"uid":38376,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T19:51:19.000Z","msg":"我前幾個月去完金門黎<br />\n<br />\n真係好靚，空氣又好，人又好，好多歷史故事可以認識，博物館，砲台，地道同歷史文物參觀點都係免費，地方樸素，人超放鬆。唯一差係冇夜市同交通唔得。<br />\n<br />\n去到廈門，空氣差到塊面搵紙巾抹係灰色，地方又污糟，然後鼓浪嶼上面乜都要收錢，砲台都要&yen;80，搭程船要排45分鐘換票同安檢，去個廈門大學又限人搞到好多人兜客&yen;100帶你入去好腐敗。唯一好係call 車方便同食野多元化。"},{"pid":"7abf6627a93a027867ee0a1547ac1d77c39cf2ff","tid":785839,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1fac3ba9bde28c5454a3f9c5997a3985850a10f","tid":785839,"uid":79190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d68a9344a30e0066031d66890064fef79825b87","tid":785839,"uid":49353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打去打工換宿係到咗埗先搵？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"通常都要早啲嘅<br />\n好似我今次要三月就遞CV比個老世話要8月黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T19:52:19.000Z","msg":"請問係幾多歲可以咁樣呢？"},{"pid":"f17506fd9bb2559fd12092678f9236530c983e1b","tid":785839,"uid":27505,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T19:56:59.000Z","msg":"其實香港都係日日打工換宿姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f987b072ef5fe710f729c5d106888bc938f58f","tid":785839,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f17506fd9bb2559fd12092678f9236530c983e1b","tid":785839,"uid":27505,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T19:56:59.000Z","msg":"其實香港都係日日打工換宿姐<